    <div class="rte">
      <h1></h1>
<h1 id="yui_3_17_2_1_1415097089802_268"></h1>
<h2><strong>Your Privacy</strong></h2>
<p><span>MJ Services is totally committed to protecting the privacy of our site, visitors and above all customers. Our employees fully appreciate and respect the importance of privacy and we will not disclose information about our customers to third parties without previously being given their permission. All personal information is protected under the Data Protection Act of 1994 of which MJ Services is registered and fully compliant.</span></p>
<p><span>We do not store credit card details nor do we share customer details with any 3rd parties.</span></p>
<p><strong><span>Your Consent</span></strong></p>
<p><span>We will not rent or sell your name, address, email address or personal information to any third party without your prior permission.</span></p>
<p><strong><span>Communications and Marketing</span></strong></p>
<p><span>We may, from time-to-time, post or email advertisements and offers which we feel may be of interest to you. If you do not wish to receive these please contact us as soon as possible.</span></p>
<p><strong><span>Contacting Us</span></strong></p>
<p><span>We are always pleased to hear from our customers and are particularly keen to hear any complaints that they may have. We are always grateful for any time you spend providing us with the feedback which is so essential for us to be able change and improve the service which we aim to offer to our customers.</span></p>
    </div>

